============
Description:
============

This is a mod for Minetest-c55 game.

Makes cement and clay from dirt. Can be used on its own but is really intended as a building
block for other mods where cement makes sense like stone masonry and concrete.


============
Dependancies:
=============

See depends.txt file.


========
Recipes:
========

Cement:
-------

1. lime
2. lime
4. sand / desert sand
5. clay

Produces 4 cement.


Clay:
-----

1. dirt / dirt with grass
2. dirt / dirt with grass
4. dirt / dirt with grass
5. dirt / dirt with grass

Produces 1 clay

